org.apache.james.mailetcontainer.impl

Class JamesMailSpooler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.mailetcontainer.impl.JamesMailSpooler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, Configurable, LogEnabled, MailSpoolerMBean

    public class JamesMailSpooler
extends Object
implements Runnable, Configurable, LogEnabled, MailSpoolerMBean
    Manages the mail spool. This class is responsible for retrieving messages from the spool, directing messages to the appropriate processor, and removing them from the spool when processing is complete.
